ing: 2 cups cubed, cooked boneless chicken breast meat
2 cups whole peeled tomatoes, with liquid
des: "Jam packed with veggies as well as chicken breast and tomatoes, this is a healthy, hearty quick stew."
ins: In a large soup pot combine the onion, chicken, celery, tomatoes with liquid, carrots, broth, corn, peas and zucchini. Stir together and simmer over medium low heat for 1/2 hour, or until vegetables are cooked and tender.
